r","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/create-a-logo","uuid":"eb6e66f0-776c-46d4-8b55-a716b220662d","anchor":null,"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"Create a logo","id":576454408,"uuid":"eb6e66f0-776c-46d4-8b55-a716b220662d","slug":"create-a-logo","url":"tools/create-a-logo/","full_slug":"tools/create-a-logo/","_stopResolving":true}}}]},{"text":". ","type":"text"}]}]}},{"_uid":"62428759-d257-411c-bfe0-fc77636f4630","icon":{"id":20716881,"alt":"","name":"","focus":"","title":"","source":"","filename":"https://a.storyblok.com/f/191576/72x72/ac2c6fb878/mobile_phone.webp","copyright":"","fieldtype":"asset","meta_data":{},"is_external_url":false,"blurDataURL":"data:image/webp;base64,UklGRnwAAABXRUJQVlA4WAoAAAAQAAAADwAADwAAQUxQSD0AAAARJ6CQbQQ4Npt7PA7iIiJ4NSiEJMmZuxN4hCQQDd4fK79ARP+FBARNc4OFtbUE+N7aUMj2vztZMf/Mf7MAAFZQOCAYAAAAMAEAnQEqEAAQAAVAfCWkAANwAP7w5sAA"},"title":"Access anywhere","component":"FeaturesListBlockItem","description":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"Edit and manage your brand’s visuals from any desktop or mobile device.","type":"text"}]}]}}],"component":"FeaturesListBlock","globalContent":"74cbf7ce-54df-4de0-9bde-9192c05de597"},{"_uid":"c5316601-266a-4b65-97a7-02979084e013","items":[{"_uid":"0306f693-4cb2-463a-8640-4eabc9a415a1","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Product Staging is an AI-powered tool that enables you to showcase your products in realistic, lifestyle scenes without the need for traditional photoshoots. By simply uploading your product photo, the tool generates contextual images that depict your item in everyday settings, enhancing visual appeal and boosting customer engagement.","type":"text"}]}]},"question":"What is Photoroom’s Product Staging?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"2630be80-c872-4266-ad8c-15f9f1e071b9","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Product Staging combines OpenAI’s GPT-Image-1 model with Photoroom’s deep expertise in visual merchandising to create realistic, context-rich scenes. Our AI analyzes your product image, automatically generating an ideal lifestyle setting that highlights real-world usage, making your visuals compelling and ready to convert. For more information check out our","type":"text"},{"text":" Help Center","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://help.photoroom.com/en/articles/11155705-show-a-product-in-a-realistic-scene-with-product-staging","uuid":null,"anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_blank","linktype":"url","rel":"noopener noreferrer"}}]},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},"question":"How does Photoroom’s Product Staging work?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"7eb787db-7aad-4e6d-84ab-2aaa44a74aa0","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Yes, Photoroom's Product Staging is designed to produce high-quality, lifestyle-oriented images that can improve product listings on various e‑commerce platforms, social media, and advertising campaigns.","type":"text"}]}]},"question":"Is Product Staging suitable for e‑commerce platforms?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"d4574787-8c58-4e81-b7a9-05359594ff36","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Photoroom's Product Staging tool automatically generates realistic lifestyle scenes for your product. While you can't select a specific background, the AI provides diverse, contextually relevant options. After generation, you can further customize the image by editing elements like ","type":"text"},{"text":"background","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/instant-backgrounds","uuid":"f06c5fbf-32b3-4356-a5c0-1f593ec27bf2","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"AI Backgrounds","id":267699872,"uuid":"f06c5fbf-32b3-4356-a5c0-1f593ec27bf2","slug":"instant-backgrounds","url":"tools/instant-backgrounds","full_slug":"tools/instant-backgrounds","_stopResolving":true}}}]},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},"question":"Can I choose the background or setting for my product?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"c077262f-009f-4c09-b158-1eb53df4d161","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"While the AI provides automatically generated backgrounds, you can further edit the images using ","type":"text"},{"text":"Photoroom's suite of tools","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools","uuid":"919448a2-b538-47ef-b3e5-30876b540c24","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"AI Photo Editor - Free Photo Editing Tools","id":593249331,"uuid":"919448a2-b538-47ef-b3e5-30876b540c24","slug":"tools","url":"tools/","full_slug":"tools/","_stopResolving":true}}}]},{"text":". This includes adjusting elements like background, adding text, or incorporating ","type":"text"},{"text":"logos","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/create-a-logo","uuid":"eb6e66f0-776c-46d4-8b55-a716b220662d","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"Create a logo","id":576454408,"uuid":"eb6e66f0-776c-46d4-8b55-a716b220662d","slug":"create-a-logo","url":"tools/create-a-logo/","full_slug":"tools/create-a-logo/","_stopResolving":true}}}]},{"text":" to better fit your brand's aesthetic.","type":"text"}]}]},"question":"Can I customize the backgrounds generated by the tool?","component":"FaqItem"}],"component":"FaqBlock","titleBlock":[{"_uid":"85dce38c-a127-4b98-9852-546118c31211","title":"Frequently asked questions","variant":"","overline":"Product Staging","component":"SectionTitle"}],"containerId":"faq-block"},{"_uid":"","limit":"10","component":"RelatedLinks","titleBlock":[{"_uid":"a11ea2eb-a73c-4e81-ad6f-5b2fc61f1ad2","title":"More AI tools for fashion product photos","variant":"","overline":"Explore","subtitle":"","component":"SectionTitle"}],"relationType":"tools"}],"component":"Page","