ic product shots into polished, studio-quality visuals with AI. Show your products in real-world environments that captivate customers and boost sales.","component":"PageTitle"}],"visual":[{"_uid":"2c4fd510-3795-4ff4-94f1-c84a901998c0","video":{"id":21958292,"alt":"","name":"","focus":"","title":"","source":"","filename":"https://a.storyblok.com/f/191576/x/f400d44149/website-productbeautifier_1.mp4","copyright":"","fieldtype":"asset","meta_data":{},"is_external_url":false},"component":"FeatureBlockClassicVisualVideo","hasOriginalAspectRatio":false}],"component":"QuickToolHeroBlock","backgroundColor":""},{"_uid":"90df1c05-a8c1-4b14-9fca-73f26eead4b0","title":[{"_uid":"48aee49a-a144-4f88-bf0e-d15d7645690b","title":"Refine your product shots instantly with AI","variant":"","overline":"Better workflow","subtitle":"","component":"SectionTitle"}],"features":[{"_uid":"826a63fd-c001-4d9a-b396-fb03aa848235","type":"","wide":true,"title":"Turn ordinary product photos into visual masterpieces","ctaLink":{"id":"","url":"","linktype":"story","fieldtype":"multilink","cached_url":"","href":""},"ctaLabel":"","component":"FeatureBlock","invertOrder":false,"visualElement":[{"_uid":"a9d03cf8-46cb-4e38-b5fa-e79edec1d2b8","image":{"id":21958315,"alt":"","name":"","focus":"","title":"","source":"","filename":"https://a.storyblok.com/f/191576/1048x786/91ed1683f2/product_beautifier_1.webp","copyright":"","fieldtype":"asset","meta_data":{},"is_external_url":false,"blurDataURL":"data:image/webp;base64,UklGRlAAAABXRUJQVlA4IEQAAADQAQCdASoQAAwABUB8JZACdADpnGuzAAD+mxLzLEukEEoJMZpkvGcBsKpGvxFpvVFFYXlry14ScjYCX8K8SKlRtgAAAA=="},"component":"FeatureBlockClassicVisualImage"}],"descriptionText":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Give your images a studio-quality finish without ever booking one. Product Beautifier automatically enhances lighting, sharpens details, and boosts color in seconds. Ideal for social posts, marketing campaigns, or any moment you want your visuals to shine.","type":"text"}]}]},"withVisualBorder":false,"visualAspectRatio":""},{"_uid":"ce4822a4-d149-4464-8364-cc198cef6463","type":"","wide":true,"title":"Achieve consistent, high-quality images quickly","ctaLink":{"id":"","url":"","linktype":"story","fieldtype":"multilink","cached_url":"","href":""},"ctaLabel":"","component":"FeatureBlock","invertOrder":true,"visualElement":[{"_uid":"a3ed112f-3d25-4ba7-b4cd-756c7475c864","image":{"id":21958261,"alt":"","name":"","focus":"","title":"","source":"","filename":"https://a.storyblok.com/f/191576/1048x786/0007634592/product_beautifier_2.webp","copyright":"","fieldtype":"asset","meta_data":{},"is_external_url":false,"blurDataURL":"data:image/webp;base64,UklGRk4AAABXRUJQVlA4IEIAAADwAQCdASoQAAwABUB8JZQAAujdPvAQ4AAA/rQPIgo8P6ApWldhjRrFOWux3/UpXjDSHY9tN0uO/ti3mOi8RiDgQAA="},"component":"FeatureBlockClassicVisualImage"}],"descriptionText":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"No experience? No problem. Create high-resolution product photos in one click. Powered by GPT-Image-1, Product Beautifier automatically fine-tunes lighting, angles, and sharpness, delivering results that rival a professional studio. Let the AI do the heavy lifting.","type":"text"}]}]},"withVisualBorder":false,"visualAspectRatio":""},{"_uid":"67c574dd-08c7-4ff2-bd5e-bd349c408e70","type":"","wide":true,"title":"Increase customer trust through high-quality visuals","ctaLink":{"id":"","url":"","linktype":"story","fieldtype":"multilink","cached_url":"","href":""},"ctaLabel":"","component":"FeatureBlock","invertOrder":false,"visualElement":[{"_uid":"3db2cf0c-ee70-47fe-8fe2-215570caebcf","image":{"id":21958264,"alt":"","name":"","focus":"","title":"","source":"","filename":"https://a.storyblok.com/f/191576/1048x786/900b9aca3d/product_beautifier_3.webp","copyright":"","fieldtype":"asset","meta_data":{},"is_external_url":false,"blurDataURL":"data:image/webp;base64,UklGRkgAAABXRUJQVlA4IDwAAACwAQCdASoQAAwABUB8JZwAAxd0zHsAAPyse2CreP1m0d4Qj389j3WNfOxxKjJXRnHlSFjaa/0Us1kAAAA="},"component":"FeatureBlockClassicVisualImage"}],"descriptionText":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Studio-quality photos aren’t just a nice-to-have, they drive clicks, conversions, and sales. Product Beautifier uses AI to turn simple shots into stunning visuals that look professionally done. Just upload your photo, and get clean, high-impact images that build trust and boost sales.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]},"withVisualBorder":false,"visualAspectRatio":""}],"component":"FeaturesBlock"},{"_uid":"5a8a8bb6-d347-4428-87d9-6951a608780c","steps":[{"_uid":"cae99683-0e3c-42fe-86b6-af363349f5de","title":"Create an account","content":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Sign up to start generating professional product images. You’ll get instant access to Product Beautifier and all other AI-powered design tools with a free trial.","type":"text"}]}]},"component":"StepItem","badgeTitle":"Step 1"},{"_uid":"c061ffb7-7808-4fab-b1f0-dcb6bb6a1459","title":"Test different ideas","content":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Navigate to the AI Tools tab and select Product Beautifier. Upload your product image. Choose your preferred image dimensions then click Generate to create two AI-enhanced versions of your photo. Select your favorite version.","type":"text"}]}]},"component":"StepItem","badgeTitle":"Step 2"},{"_uid":"606af4dc-589d-4ca7-ab2f-dda1b988f276","title":"Download your image","content":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"text":"Download your polished, studio-quality image as a PNG or JPEG, ready for use across all platforms. You can also refine your image using other Photoroom's tools.","type":"text"}]}]},"component":"StepItem","badgeTitle":"Step 3"}],"component":"StepsBlock","titleBlock":[{"_uid":"9c5df2ad-704a-4fa4-8fe3-32b25129e03a","title":"How to use Product Beautifier","variant":"","overline":"Try it yourself","subtitle":"","component":"SectionTitle"}]},{"_uid":"0da2acef-8e99-48cc-8de9-202a85550ed2","title":[{"_uid":"5e796e0d-8360-4409-b07e-e2add67a6e36","title":"All the AI product photography tools you need","variant":"","overline":"A complete solution","subtitle":"Keep your brand looking sharp and consistent with Photoroom’s AI product photography tools.","component":"SectionTitle"}],"features":[{"_uid":"72135771-3d9b-490c-baf3-0d8cf257761b","icon":{"id":20716724,"alt":"","name":"","focus":"","title":"","source":"","filename":"https://a.storyblok.com/f/191576/72x72/6cb0526520/remove_background.webp","copyright":"","fieldtype":"asset","meta_data":{},"is_external_url":false,"blurDataURL":"data:image/webp;base64,UklGRpgAAABXRUJQVlA4WAoAAAAQAAAADwAADwAAQUxQSFoAAAARL6CmbSM4WiSduz93h+IiIsB7GawiSXYyVTh4T0Hi/0UDBAMX/MsBCRH9nwC+i7v7CTvnnBVOAPmhv3POabG/99qPRc7RQhTYR+nJYLcQh8CeV64K4u5+8h1WUDggGAAAADABAJ0BKhAAEAAFQHwlpAADcAD+8ObAAA=="},"title":"Erase photo backgrounds","component":"FeaturesListBlockItem","description":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"Instantly ","type":"text"},{"text":"remove","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/background-remover","uuid":"44fff530-e568-41f1-90c9-ce31cdf7fa99","anchor":null,"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"Background Remover","id":343576837,"uuid":"44fff530-e568-41f1-90c9-ce31cdf7fa99","slug":"background-remover","url":"tools/background-remover/","full_slug":"tools/background-remover/","_stopResolving":true}}},{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":""}},{"type":"underline"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/background-remover","uuid":"44fff530-e568-41f1-90c9-ce31cdf7fa99","anchor":null,"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"Background Remover","id":343576837,"uuid":"44fff530-e568-41f1-90c9-ce31cdf7fa99","slug":"background-remover","url":"tools/background-remover/","full_slug":"tools/backgro