9bde-9192c05de597"},{"_uid":"c5316601-266a-4b65-97a7-02979084e013","items":[{"_uid":"8d3af6fb-6594-458c-aabc-1c578ae1d9a3","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"An AI virtual model generator uses generative AI to place clothing and other fashion items like jewelry, eyewear, and footwear onto lifelike digital models. With Photoroom, you can upload a product image, choose your preferred model type, and our AI automatically creates high-quality virtual model images with natural poses and lighting.","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]}]}]},"question":"How does an AI virtual model generator work for clothing and fashion photos?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"2630be80-c872-4266-ad8c-15f9f1e071b9","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"Yes, you can easily generate virtual fashion models wearing your brand’s products. Upload a photo of your clothing item: a dress, a top, a pair of jeans, or whatever you sell, and Photoroom’s AI model generator automatically places it on a realistic model. ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]}]}]},"question":"Can I use AI to create virtual models wearing my brand’s products?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"7a55f0c3-1c12-44c8-a2a8-96b9df225acb","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"Photoroom’s AI fashion model generator is the best solution for e‑commerce and fashion lookbooks. We combine AI virtual model generation with ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]},{"text":"background removal","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/background-remover","uuid":"44fff530-e568-41f1-90c9-ce31cdf7fa99","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"Background Remover","id":343576837,"uuid":"44fff530-e568-41f1-90c9-ce31cdf7fa99","slug":"background-remover","url":"tools/background-remover/","full_slug":"tools/background-remover/","_stopResolving":true}}},{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#1155CC"}},{"type":"underline"}]},{"text":" and ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]},{"text":"background generation","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/instant-backgrounds","uuid":"f06c5fbf-32b3-4356-a5c0-1f593ec27bf2","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"AI Backgrounds","id":267699872,"uuid":"f06c5fbf-32b3-4356-a5c0-1f593ec27bf2","slug":"instant-backgrounds","url":"tools/instant-backgrounds","full_slug":"tools/instant-backgrounds","_stopResolving":true}}},{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#1155CC"}},{"type":"underline"}]},{"text":", ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]},{"text":"lighting adjustment","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools/image-brightener","uuid":"8d8bd629-735e-47f3-8ab5-f7f70cdda0e0","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"Image Brightener","id":356367864,"uuid":"8d8bd629-735e-47f3-8ab5-f7f70cdda0e0","slug":"image-brightener","url":"tools/image-brightener","full_slug":"tools/image-brightener","_stopResolving":true}}},{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#1155CC"}},{"type":"underline"}]},{"text":", and more ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]},{"text":"AI photo editing tools","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/tools","uuid":"919448a2-b538-47ef-b3e5-30876b540c24","anchor":null,"custom":{},"target":"_self","linktype":"story","story":{"name":"AI Photo Editor - Free Photo Editing Tools","id":593249331,"uuid":"919448a2-b538-47ef-b3e5-30876b540c24","slug":"tools","url":"tools/","full_slug":"tools/","_stopResolving":true}}},{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#1155CC"}},{"type":"underline"}]},{"text":" to help you create high-quality, consistent, and affordable e‑commerce visuals at scale.","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]}]}]},"question":"What’s the best AI fashion model generator for e‑commerce or lookbooks?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"a1f21ea8-ba0a-49ec-8900-bc1306eae535","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"AI virtual model tools are trained on natural poses, lighting, backgrounds, and material textures to produce realistic results that match the look and feel of a professional fashion photo shoot. With Photoroom, you can choose model styles, backgrounds, poses, and image dimensions, ensuring your AI fashion photography looks realistic, diverse, and on-brand.","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]}]}]},"question":"How realistic are AI-generated models compared to real photoshoots?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"bf49aa86-6661-4461-9c5a-c729107eff97","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"Photoroom’s virtual model tool uses generative AI to automatically place clothing items on photorealistic models, adjust shadows and textures for accuracy, and create cohesive imagery for all your sales channels. ","type":"text","marks":[{"type":"textStyle","attrs":{"color":"#000000"}}]}]}]},"question":" How does Photoroom’s AI virtual model generator help fashion brands create realistic product photos?","component":"FaqItem"},{"_uid":"cfff0380-2db1-4630-8cf9-f9f19dfafa01","answer":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"text":"Yes. Virtual Model is fully accessible via the Photoroom API, allowing enterprise teams to integrate model photography directly into their existing workflows and automate it across their entire product catalogue.","type":"text"}]}]},"question":"Is Virtual Model part of the Photoroom API?","component":"